OL,4,CSchool abuse: Teachers face sexualised
OL,5,Cinsults in class, says union
OL,6, Teachers face "derogatory sexualised"
OL,7, language as well as violence and
OL,8, threats from pupils in the classroom, a
OL,9, union conference has heard.
OL,11,FThe NASUWT conference condemned schools
OL,12,Fand colleges that claim "unacceptable"
OL,13,Fstudent behaviour is "part of the job".
OL,15,FA survey of over 4,700 union members
OL,16,Ffound 38% had been verbally abused, and
OL,17,F10% threatened with violence.
OL,19,F"We need to reclaim our classrooms, but
OL,20,Fwe cannot do it alone," said NASUWT
OL,21,Fexecutive member Wendy Exton.
